<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:03D687E03C0DC4785BB77EFB2E05FC7E:8EA0602D3C0BC4785E097D842AF9FC26" box="[1334,1447,914,940]" county="Basey" municipality="Although" name="Therefore" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" stateProvince="Samar">Therefore</location>
